com.github.gwtbootstrap.client.ui.Nav.setAlignment(String)
          This method should never be called directly. It will break your implementation if any style names change. The only valid use is inside UiBinder files where it processes the alignment="..." argument. Use Nav.setAlignment(Alignment) instead!
